{"tid":256916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤信「英籍水手」遭海盜掠劫　港女墮騙局索償245萬","createTime":"2017-05-25T00:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T00:21:16.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"211180ff9840147f5a03fb23597319233f790908","tid":256916,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170524/_2017052416193668048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170524%2F_2017052416193668048.jpg&h=b67a9c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子及後發現香港並無內政部，墜入網絡騙案，向三間公司索償。<br />\n<br />\n港女聲稱去年暑假在網上結識一名英國籍水手男，男方稱船隻受海盜掠劫，於是委托馬來西亞保安公司將個人行裝運來香港，港女同意協助接收該包裹，但是後來保安公司以不同籍口要求港女付款，如海關懷疑貨物是賊贓、馬國政府懷疑她贊助恐怖襲撃等，又揚言已向「香港內政部」報案。女子驚訝下向三個戶口存入共約245萬港元，終發現香港並無內政部，墜入網絡騙案。港女於是入稟高院向三間公司索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告何志穎Belinda（譯音），被告依次是馬來西亞保安公司Secure Dip-Sea Security Company及兩間香港公司深圳市豐鼎盛實業有限公司和深圳市信浩騰科技有限公司。入稟狀指，港女在網上認識自稱英國水手的Anthony Richard，雙方以電郵溝通，在水手要求下同意協助收貨，她按指示提供了個人身份資料及2250美元運費。<br />\n<br />\n但是去9月，首被告指馬來西亞海關懷疑包裹內有黑錢，或涉及恐怖襲撃，要求她支付7750美元，否則會「身陷險境」。隔一個月又指馬來西亞政府懷疑她贊助恐怖襲撃，要求她支付22900美元。再隔一個月，又指當局通報了「香港內政部」，再多次索取款項。港女後來發現墜入欺詐騙局並報警。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：方嘉欣<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/911352/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F911352%2F&d=uZoqg%2FSeSQPAeDQzWqixifjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=2d9a48b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F911352%2F&h=3092b76c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/911352/</a>"},{"pid":"14e7efc209d65b36cf840ea25a2a5659f1e436fa","tid":256916,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:10:42.000Z","msg":"😂😂😂😂😂😂😂🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣"},{"pid":"0860788ffcdac8c0314d78aea6cf4807a994010b","tid":256916,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"c465a67054f9d6e04b4cada18bd2af45f24dcb6d","tid":256916,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9a325bfa056d99b0f3d9c7d2ec64872e8655d5c","tid":256916,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"洋腸陷阱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9323fae561085090970179eefc836a7081a5218","tid":256916,"uid":72512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:13:28.000Z","msg":"點解比人呃果D全部都咁有錢"},{"pid":"1d2269740edbc4498619b89921d4537265047670","tid":256916,"uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:13:49.000Z","msg":"英名名係笨撚旦?<br />\n不怕塊田臭，最怕改壞名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535f3640f1143beb1f01474e2c7192ae3226b717","tid":256916,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解比人呃果D全部都咁有錢</blockquote><br />\n冇錢點畀人呃"},{"pid":"01dd28a387af99f0aa7cdc714b41cf83e0a9c110","tid":256916,"uid":57504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"Anthony Richard, 個水手名好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}